  },
  {
    "row": 54,
    "rowsha": "/TS46DQEMxxwnmfnVhchX7kMJqgM12SZ5HK0RJqxpzs=",
    "originContent": "NOTE: YOU MUST DELETE ALL INSTANCES OF .gitignore OTHERWISE WHATEVER YOU COMPILE WITH WONT SEE THE FILES IN THE AREAS THEY ARE IN.",
    "translatedContent": "注意：你必须删除所有的 .gitignore 文件，否则你编译的内容将无法识别它们所在区域的文件。"
  },
  {
    "row": 55,
    "rowsha": "Za7xrbqGcqX+eTLZ+fDcNcJDWJP2URKsrGKNLcF6C88=",
    "originContent": "<br>",
    "translatedContent": "<br>"
  },
  {
    "row": 56,
    "rowsha": "+pz6xBZRZYN926Xokd3PJqHB6RkU0OB4NTBp8SXZaaY=",
    "originContent": "NOTE: YOU MUST INSTALL <a href=\"https://git-scm.com/install/windows\">GIT</a> BEFORE INSTALLING THE REXGLUE-SDK, OR BUILDING THIS REPO.",
    "translatedContent": "注意：你必须先安装 <a href=\"https://git-scm.com/install/windows\">GIT</a>，然后才能安装 REXGLUE-SDK 或构建此仓库。"
  },
  {
    "row": 57,
    "rowsha": "Za7xrbqGcqX+eTLZ+fDcNcJDWJP2URKsrGKNLcF6C88=",
    "originContent": "<br>",
    "translatedContent": "<br>"
  },
  {
    "row": 58,
    "rowsha": "JslY9yk2p8piWTzIlbRAl9ICPCsLrNDc/jg1OsDHVYY=",
    "originContent": "NOTE: NOTE: YOU MUST BUILD AND INSTALL THE MAIN REPO OF <a href=\"https://github.com/rexglue/rexglue-sdk\">Rexglue-SDK</a> BEFORE CONTINUING",
    "translatedContent": "注意：注意：你必须先构建并安装 <a href=\"https://github.com/rexglue/rexglue-sdk\">Rexglue-SDK</a> 主仓库，然后才能继续。"
  },
  {
    "row": 59,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 60,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 61,
    "rowsha": "lP6OJbCTosyYNzKhLdALxjndaj9GHf2BPaxBhzhUEAE=",
    "originContent": "1. Clone the repository with ```git clone https://github.com/masterspike52/reNut.git```",
    "translatedContent": "1. 使用 ```git clone https://github.com/masterspike52/reNut.git``` 克隆仓库"
  },
  {
    "row": 62,
    "rowsha": "og31ryh6/kayw8o9LQ/gNOvene6mphkU1zJg2grem4E=",
    "originContent": "2. Inside the assets folder you need to extract your banjo-kazooie: Nuts&Bolts iso's contents and the default.xex. I reccomend using <a href=\"https://consolemods.org/wiki/images/5/5f/XBOX360_ISO_Extract.zip\">iso extract</a>. (I don't know what linux users use. I use Windows, however iso extract does work on linux through WINE.)",
    "translatedContent": "2. 在 assets 文件夹内需要提取你的《Banjo-Kazooie: Nuts & Bolts》ISO 内容和 default.xex。推荐使用 <a href=\"https://consolemods.org/wiki/images/5/5f/XBOX360_ISO_Extract.zip\">iso extract</a>。（我不知道 Linux 用户用什么。我用 Windows，不过 iso extract 通过 WINE 也能在 Linux 上运行。）"
  },
  {
    "row": 63,
    "rowsha": "e729mZeFxUZ09vmRNh1A1LVjazGZuc/WdtViQQRcKn0=",
    "originContent": "3. Inside your cloned git open a terminal and run ```rexglue migrate --app_root .``` This ensures that if anything with codegen changes on Rexglue, you can codegen properly.",
    "translatedContent": "3. 在你克隆的 git 仓库中打开终端，运行 ```rexglue migrate --app_root .```。这确保如果 Rexglue 的 codegen 有任何变化，你可以正确生成代码。"
  },
  {
    "row": 64,
    "rowsha": "S3RlAXfqLjP1Bf/ARXCzZEXm6gfe5vXSuAqob1W6+UE=",
    "originContent": "   3b. You must then either delete your out folder, or if your on Windows you can open VS, right click your cmakelists.txt, and delete cache and reconfigure so you codegen with the version your using.",
    "translatedContent": "   3b. 之后你必须删除 out 文件夹，或者如果你用的是 Windows，可以打开 VS，右键点击 cmakelists.txt，删除缓存并重新配置，以便使用你当前版本的 codegen。"
  },
  {
    "row": 65,
    "rowsha": "54MO5KAEtAmCduIfp24h115ZRKN5/6BXeleiWqYVgqI=",
    "originContent": "4. You can now open a terminal and run ```rexglue codegen renut_config.toml``` which will give you the ppc files to recompile in the generated folder.",
    "translatedContent": "4. 现在你可以打开终端，运行 ```rexglue codegen renut_config.toml```，这会生成用于重新编译的 ppc 文件，位于 generated 文件夹中。"
  },
  {
    "row": 66,
    "rowsha": "r7PuLSAZz4f1Cjv0Y8m7RY5CAh6Uit35xLdtWzgPhRg=",
    "originContent": "5. If you're on Windows, you can open the project in VS, change the build type to `win-amd64-relwithdebinfo`, then build all.",
    "translatedContent": "5. 如果你用的是 Windows，可以在 VS 中打开项目，将构建类型改为 `win-amd64-relwithdebinfo`，然后全部构建。"
  },
  {
    "row": 67,
    "rowsha": "+1k3CavE+XwFpeGG6XK2yilnSzVuQBvlC1Zvg9RfCzc=",
    "originContent": "   5b. If you're on Linux, and don't have access to VS, you will need to use a terminal and run ```cmake --preset linux-amd64-relwithdebinfo``` and then ```cmake --build --preset linux-amd64-relwithdebinfo```. (You can do this on Windows as well, just replace `linux` with `windows`.)",
    "translatedContent": "   5b. 如果你用的是 Linux，且没有 VS，你需要使用终端运行 ```cmake --preset linux-amd64-relwithdebinfo```，然后运行 ```cmake --build --preset linux-amd64-relwithdebinfo```。（你也可以在 Windows 上这样做，只需将 `linux` 替换为 `windows`。）"
  },
  {
    "row": 68,
    "rowsha": "4Po6rQlnVp87APNkj8xuWQqPAN4TpA+AlSBoy1//YBQ=",
    "originContent": "6. Once its compiled, you need to have the built exe in the same directory as the assets, otherwise the game won't open.",
    "translatedContent": "6. 编译完成后，需将生成的 exe 放在与 assets 相同的目录，否则游戏无法启动。"
  },
  {
    "row": 69,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 70,
