  },
  {
    "row": 77,
    "rowsha": "9lv970Vwi28CFF1DKp/v3EvowrTO/1Dtowbn0eT0Hts=",
    "originContent": "Building is mainly for those who either would rather build or want to help develop the game with myself and others. If you don't want to build;",
    "translatedContent": "构建主要面向那些更愿意自己构建或者想与我和其他人一起开发游戏的用户。如果你不想构建；"
  },
  {
    "row": 78,
    "rowsha": "HSn3IoOibslayBS6c7KYDcXkd/G3RpbWeBx1pi8xHis=",
    "originContent": "* Go to https://goopie.xyz/ and download the goopie launcher ",
    "translatedContent": "* 访问 https://goopie.xyz/ 并下载 goopie 启动器"
  },
  {
    "row": 79,
    "rowsha": "hj1RyH8QFcfZeFxnc9pmWvuemn63KDhtQYviViPnaW4=",
    "originContent": "* In the launcher select banjo-kazooie: nuts and bolts",
    "translatedContent": "* 在启动器中选择《Banjo-Kazooie: Nuts and Bolts》"
  },
